quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,7,"By the heaven full of paths,"
  51,8,"Certainly, you have different ideas (about Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم and the Qur’ân)."
  51,9,"Turned aside therefrom (i.e. from Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم and the Qur’ân) is he who is turned aside (by the Decree and Preordainment القضاء والقدر of Allâh)."
  51,10,"Cursed be the liars"